[assistant] 
[assistant] Changes in:
[assistant] 
[assistant] `tests/src/org.apache.pekko/pekko-slf4j_2.13/1.6.0/src/test/scala/org_apache_pekko/pekko_slf4j_2_13/Pekko_slf4j_2_13Test.scala`
[assistant] 
[assistant] Fixes:
[assistant] 
