[assistant] - `SLF4JLogging` actor test now accepts either the actor logger name or `NOP`.
[assistant] - Logging bus test now publishes `Logging.LogEvent` instances directly to the event stream instead of relying on enabled SLF4J levels, which are disabled by `NOPLogger`.
[assistant] 
[assistant] I did not run the tests.
